<!doctype html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Sikeres regisztráció</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f6f7fb;">
    <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111827;">
        <div style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;">
            <h1 style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:20px;line-height:28px;">Sikeres regisztráció</h1>
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;">
                Szia <strong><%= name %></strong>!
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;">
                A regisztrációd sikeres volt. Az alábbi adatokat rögzítettük:
            </p>

            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:14px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;">Név</td>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;"><%= name %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;">Email</td>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;"><%= email %></td>
                </tr>
                <% if (backupEmail) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;">Másodlagos email</td>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;"><%= backupEmail %></td>
                </tr>
                <% } %>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;">Telefon</td>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;"><%= phone %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;color:#6b7280;">Cím</td>
                    <td style="padding:8px 0;"><%= address %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <p style="margin:16px 0 0 0;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;color:#6b7280;">
                Biztonsági okokból a jelszavadat nem küldjük el emailben.
            </p>
        </div>

        <p style="margin:12px 0 0 0;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#9ca3af;">
            Küldés ideje: <%= createdAt.toLocaleString('hu-HU') %>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
